# Installation
$ pip install flask

# Writing the flask code
Prefer atom or sublime text for writing the flask code

# Running the Website
if spyder:
          open the terminal
          cd "path where the "MyBlog" Folder is saved"
          python app.py
          you'll receive the url
if conda:
          open the conda prompt
          cd "path where the "MyBlog" Folder is saved"
          python app.py
          you'll receive the url
          
